item.title: CVE-2023-48389|2024-08-02T21:30:34.566Z -- multisuns -- easylog%20web%2B
item.description: Multisuns EasyLog web+ has a path traversal vulnerability within its parameter in a specific URL. An unauthenticated remote attacker can exploit this vulnerability to bypass authentication and download arbitrary system files.
